high_descs: Go forward then turn left then make a right to face the dresser.
Pick up the pen off of the dresser.
Turn around completely and go forward. Turn to the right ad go to the side table.
Place the pen in the mug on the side table.
Pick up the mug from the side table.
Turn to the right then go forward. Turn to the left and go back to the dresser.
Place the mug and pen on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Move a pen and mug to a dresser.

high_descs: Take a left at the end of the windows, turn right at the end of the bend and walk to the white shelf ahead.
Pick up the black pen in front of the plant on the shelf.
Turn around, take a right at the black chair and turn right at the wall to face the small round table.
Put the pen inside the white mug in front of the small lamp on the table.
Pick up the mug with the pen inside from the table.
Turn right, hang a left at the black chair and walk to the white shelf ahead.
Put the mug with the pen inside on the shelf in front of the small yellow pencil.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a pen on a shelf.

high_descs: Make a left and then hang a right to reach the desk space where the plant is.
Pick up the pen from in front of the potted plant.
Walk around the bed to reach the nightstand.
Put the pen in the cup on the nightstand.
Pick up the cup with the pen in it from the nightstand.
Hang a left around the bed to reach the desk space.
Put the cup with the pen in it in front of the yellow pencil on the desk space.
anns.task_desc: Put a pen in a cup to move them to the desk.
